# Meeter

Meeter is a simple dating application built as a technical assessment using Laravel, Vue 3, Inertia.js, Tailwind CSS, and Docker.

## Tech Stack

- Laravel 12
- Vue 3
- Inertia.js
- Tailwind CSS
- MySQL
- Docker & Docker Compose
- Vite

---

## Features

- User Registration & Login
- User Profiles
- Browse People
- Search Users
- Direct Messaging
- Conversation List
- Message History
- Responsive UI

---

